snippet.title: TheEricButts
snippet.description:
Started YouTube for  fun in 2015 & it became my job! I've now cut back to only 14 videos a week & have gone back to making music & movies again! I'm high energy! I talk fast! I talk a lot! I geek out all over the place & feel no shame about it! I Curse & I drink in my videos, but I'm always nice...mostly! 

Currently putting out a brand new, high energy, pop-punk/Garage Rock single every Friday for a while! Look up Eric Butts everywhere music is!

Release schedule:
Trailer Reaction EVERYDAY! 10AM EST
Throw Down Thursday Let's Plays with Mary! Every Thursday at 2PM EST

Get more Content as a channel member!
Disney+ Star Wars & Marvel Reviews, Movie Review, Let's Plays, Vlogs, Cooking & more! Currently putting out 6 videos a week for "Super Supporter God" tier & up!


I'm hoping with this channel to create a community where we can all feel completely free & safe to be the unabashed nerds we all truly are! If it's not a topic that makes me geek out, I'll support your geek out over it!
